100
00:07:36,665 --> 00:07:40,042
<i>When will my life begin?</i>

101
00:07:42,003 --> 00:07:45,422
<i>Tomorrow night</i>

102
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:49,760
<i>the lights will appear</i>

103
00:07:50,470 --> 00:07:53,722
<i>Just like they do</i>

104
00:07:53,807 --> 00:07:58,644
<i>on my birthday each year</i>

105
00:08:00,146 --> 00:08:03,440
<i>What is it like</i>

106
00:08:04,526 --> 00:08:08,445
<i>out there where they glow</i>

107
