(SCOFFS) Why, Rapunzel...

181
00:12:54,357 --> 00:12:57,276
(SINGING) Look at you,
<i>as fragile as a flower</i>

182
00:12:57,986 --> 00:13:01,822
<i>Still a little sapling, just a sprout</i>

183
00:13:01,906 --> 00:13:04,741
<i>You know why we stay up in this tower</i>

184
00:13:04,826 --> 00:13:06,410
- I know, but...
- That's right.

185
00:13:06,494 --> 00:13:10,372
